{"tid":2120785,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"研究指患者僅呼吸說話足以播毒","createTime":"2020-07-23T01:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T01:56:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"94e3cfd1b7931aefa2eb9c5e57a01563d2129de9","tid":2120785,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:56:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200723/AMYRVBMCZIFGQBHWSHT2HGMPEQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200723%2FAMYRVBMCZIFGQBHWSHT2HGMPEQ%2F&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgAx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=7f0ad79b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200723%2FAMYRVBMCZIFGQBHWSHT2HGMPEQ%2F&h=f893f908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200723/AMYRVBMCZIFGQBHWSHT2HGMPEQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n研究指患者僅呼吸說話足以播毒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/axYFOoqrxH3NgN_ql2DelTctnt8=/190x125/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KSV4UXQLTYFDVE36BT4YR4JPWE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaxYFOoqrxH3NgN_ql2DelTctnt8%3D%2F190x125%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKSV4UXQLTYFDVE36BT4YR4JPWE.gif&h=1da214e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n研究指呼吸產生的微飛沫已可播毒。<br />\n<br />\n美國一項研究證實，武肺患者呼吸或說話時釋放的微飛沬可傳播病毒。內布拉斯加大學的研究首次發現，體積小於五微米的微飛沫可在實驗室中再生，助證了不只是咳嗽和打噴嚏，正常呼吸和說話也可傳播病毒，而病毒移動的距離遠超於兩米。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美累計390萬宗確診 單日死者再破千<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n微飛沫傳播 距離遠超兩米<br />\n<br />\n團隊在五間病房中以離地約30厘米的距離採集樣本。病人說話時產生的微飛沫在空氣中懸浮數小時，即外界所指的「氣霧」，加上有部份病人咳嗽。內布拉斯加大學醫學中心。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n團隊把樣本在實驗室中培植，在18個樣本中發現有三個可自行再生。桑塔皮亞指這代表微飛沫有傳染力。研究結果僅為初步，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n科學界一度否定病毒透過微飛沫傳播的可能性，世界衞生組織（WHO）至本月初才改變立場。桑塔皮亞直斥討論「被政治凌駕科學」，「我認為大部份研究傳染病的科學家都同意病毒有可。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法新社"}]}